<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cadastro</title>
    <script src="/js/cadastro.js" defer></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/cadastro_rest.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <h3>Sua empresa necessita de uma gestão ágil?</h3>
        <div class="cadastro-holder">
            <form id="cadastroForm" class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between p-5" action="/cadastro" method="post">
                <h3>Registre-se para nunca mais passar fome!</h2>

                <div class="form-inputs d-flex flex-column mt-4">
                    <input  type="text" placeholder="Nome Completo" name="user_name" id="user_name">
                    <input class="mt-4" type="text" placeholder="Celular" name="user_phone" id="user_phone">
                    <input class="mt-4" type="password" placeholder="Senha" name="user_pw" id="user_pw">
                    <input class="mt-4" type="text" placeholder="Email" name="user_email" id="user_email">
                </div>

                <button class="mt-5">Cadastreoihuioyhb-se</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
    <img src="../../img/cadastro/cadastroBg.svg" id="bgImg" alt="">
</body>
</html>